e=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Dez 27, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104nbo1665702702246.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/nbo1665702702246.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/nbo1665702702246.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"nbo1665702702246\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Delete Constraint </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Defines Uniface behavior when an occurrence of the One Entity is deleted, and there\n      are related occurrences of the many entity available in the component data structure. Valid\n      values are <code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">Restricted</code> (default),\n         <code class=\"ph codeph\">Cascading</code>, or <code class=\"ph codeph\">Nullify</code>. </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"nbo1665702702246__section_w1295ab1b5b1_w1296ab1b5_w1297ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"nbo1665702702246__table_d11072e1_d11073e1_d11074e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"nbo1665702702246__table_d11072e1_d11073e1_d11074e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Value</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"nbo1665702702246__table_d11072e1_d11073e1_d11074e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Description</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nbo1665702702246__table_d11072e1_d11073e1_d11074e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">Restricted</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nbo1665702702246__table_d11072e1_d11073e1_d11074e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">An occurrence of the One Entity cannot be deleted if there are\n                           occurrences of the Many Entity with a matching foreign key.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nbo1665702702246__table_d11072e1_d11073e1_d11074e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">Cascading</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nbo1665702702246__table_d11072e1_d11073e1_d11074e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">If an occurrence of the One Entity is deleted, all occurrences in the\n                           Many Entity that have a matching foreign keys are also deleted.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nbo1665702702246__table_d11072e1_d11073e1_d11074e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">Nullify</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nbo1665702702246__table_d11072e1_d11073e1_d11074e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">If an occurrence of the One Entity is deleted, the foreign key value of\n                           occurrences in the Many Entity that have a matching foreign key is set to\n                           NULL.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"nbo1665702702246__section_vts_kyr_4wb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d138182e148\">Applies To</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"nbo1665702702246__ul_n2r_lyr_4wb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"nbo1665702702246__li_d39683e1_d39684e1_d39685e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xtb1665702702029.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xtb1665702702029.html\" title=\"A Relationship is a Development Object that represents an association between one entity and another. It specifies the primary or candidate keys to be used in maintaining the association, as well as the delete constraints to be used when deleting occurrences in the related entities.\">Relationship</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fnf1665702703926.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Referential Integrity</a><p>Referential integrity is a standard feature of relational database design that prevents users or applications from entering inconsistent data. Most relational databases have referential integrity rules that you can apply when you create a relationship between tables.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/eei1704363244858.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Relationships</a><p>A relationship is an association between one entity and another. It is modeled as a development object belonging to the many-side entity in a one-to-many relationship.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3614742\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3614742\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Delete Constraint Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Dez 27, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Delete Constraint Defines Uniface behavior when an occurrence of the One Entity is deleted, and there are related occurrences of the many entity available in the component data structure. Valid values are Restricted (default), Cascading , or Nullify . Value Description Restricted An occurrence of the One Entity cannot be deleted if there are occurrences of the Many Entity with a matching foreign key. Cascading If an occurrence of the One Entity is deleted, all occurrences in the Many Entity that have a matching foreign keys are also deleted. Nullify If an occurrence of the One Entity is deleted, the foreign key value of occurrences in the Many Entity that have a matching foreign key is set to NULL. Applies To Relationship Related Links Referential Integrity Referential integrity is a standard feature of relational database design that prevents users or applications from entering inconsistent data. Most relational databases have referential integrity rules that you can apply when you create a relationship between tables. Relationships A relationship is an association between one entity and another. It is modeled as a development object belonging to the many-side entity in a one-to-many relationship. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}